  • Classes in de.db.derpate.persistence used by de.db.derpate.persistence 
    Class Description
    Dao
    Interface each data access object should implement, including methods to find an entry by id, list all entities, persist/update/remove an entity.
    EmailPasswordLoginUserDao
    Abstract Data Access Object, that can be used for all objects, that extend EmailPasswordLoginUser, to get their id, email and password
    EntityManagerFactory
    This factory uses java's Persistence class to create an EntityManagerFactory and EntityManager's using the persistence settings file (src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml).
    Pattern: Singleton
    IdDao
    Data Access Object, that can be used for all models, that extend from Id
